牌？</blockquote><br />\n要，都係分筆試同路試 筆試會問你點樣照顧隻牛 點樣知道隻牛心情 ， 之前路試派左隻閪牛比我 騎上去踢極都唔郁搞到fail左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難考過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次派左去塔門考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係係到食草唔比我騎之後衰左要游水返元朗搵過隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我路試都fail過2次<br />\n一次泊極都泊唔好隻牛 <br />\n另一次係控制唔到隻牛，我一路騎佢佢一路屙屎。<br />\n所以話 派到隻好牛真係好重要<br />\n筆試輕鬆滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61276655b3e5822ec589611c79136561b69b4711","tid":230010,"uid":93629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都想試吓去騎牛，使唔使考牌？</blockquote><br />\n要，都係分筆試同路試 筆試會問你點樣照顧隻牛 點樣知道隻牛心情 ， 之前路試派左隻閪牛比我 騎上去踢極都唔郁搞到fail左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難考過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次派左去塔門考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係係到食草唔比我騎之後衰左要游水返元朗搵過隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我路試都fail過2次<br />\n一次泊極都泊唔好隻牛 <br />\n另一次係控制唔到隻牛，我一路騎佢佢一路屙屎。<br />\n所以話 派到隻好牛真係好重要<br />\n筆試輕鬆滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你騎之瓶要先用乾草炆一炆佢屎眼<br />\n隻牛覺得你玩佢屎眼就會驚<br />\n佢全程都會聽曬你話<br />\n利申六年前騎牛筆試路試一剔PASS<br />\n前年考埋國際騎牛牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b0bd86216860cf402b8bd5c9b3ca7b4abb48b1","tid":230010,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"屋企有3部牛堡堅尼 5部牛拉利啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ef9dbd3ce9b654ba33707e6ab977a4fb944364","tid":230010,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":